    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are people to call but it feels so performative like... they just want to fix me so i'm easier for society to deal with. it doesn't change the fact that being who i actually am feels like a life sentence of being hated or misunderstood. i'm just so tired of the struggle.",
